  "texts": [
    "In the study of Ali and Mallaiah [61], CNN and SVM were combined, following [55] [56] (see Sect. 3.2.3).",
    "SVM was chosen over other ML classifiers experimentally, providing the best accuracy in comparisons.",
    "For feature extraction, two deep neural network models, Spatial Pyramid Pooling (SPPnet) and Network in Network (NIN), were integrated Simultaneously.",
    "Cross-entropy and max-margin minimum classification error (M3CE) were merged to enhance results.",
    "Results demonstrated the effectiveness of dropout as well as the capacity of M3CE to develop cross-entropy."
  ],
